					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You set the palette by setting the PPU data location to $3F00 and writing the 32 bytes of the palette. You set the scroll with registers $2005, and $2000. You enable rendering with $2001. It's all on the wiki:<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers</a><!-- m --></div>

